commit 849f4f8757173fbe0e63c0ae21f23123bf9defb1
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2011-06-22 20:37:24 +0200

    macplus: Post disk insertion events correctly
    
    The high word of the event message of a disk insertion event must
    be zero. This fixes the problem that a disk would sometimes be
    ejected immediatly after being inserted.

