Date:   2011-05-27 09:52:32 +0200

    macplus: Add ADB callback functions shift_in() and shift_out()
    
    Communication between the ADB transceiver and the VIA are now
    handled by callback functions, better separating the ADB
    implementation from the rest of the system.

