Date:   2010-09-12 00:17:58 +0200

    hgc: Support unmapping page 1
    
    The second page at B800:0000 should be unmapped when it is disabled.
    
    This patch also removes support for specifying the HGC video RAM
    size. This was never a useful option.

commit a40aef3c774ba272193151c78c4cadc188599cdd
