commit 946d304c5734aa7e155b57d408ac41189f181e07
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2010-08-12 17:09:58 +0200

    8086: Fix leaving the halt state
    
    In halt mode we need to keep checking for interrupts. When an interrupt
    arrives, it must be serviced immediatly, before executing the next
    instruction.

