commit 2cfb13a3ddcfb268dc7708f2e447b456caef1357
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-12-08 05:36:38 +0100

    configure: Fix reporting of posix file character driver detection
    
    If the posix file character driver was not explicitly enabled or
    disabled, it was always reported as not detected. Only the
    reporting was broken, the character driver was still enabled
    or disabled correctly.

