Date:   2009-11-26 14:17:06 +0100

    ibmpc: Support PCM cassette files
    
    Raw PCM files (8 bit signed at 44100Hz) can now be read and written
    directly. PCM mode is selected in the config file or with the new
    message "emu.tape.pcm".

