Date:   2009-10-29 20:49:40 +0100

    macplus: Reset the clock sync before running
    
    The real time clock sync needs to be reset before the emulation
    is started from the monitor.

commit 951e1d2495887c5ccbd41670b711fbf7ce2e0c05
