Date:   2009-10-27 17:59:36 +0100

    macplus: Fix clocking of the SCC
    
    The SCC clock should be derived from real time, not the emulated
    CPU clock.

commit c1532982edf09fc206249386afd60c9920bfdae6
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
