    8530: Implement transmission rate control

commit 564c9f833bd17ccac4032f19caabcc5cfbf979dc
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-26 15:50:36 +0100

    macplus: Better synchronization with real time

commit 1293fd2116ba09e4847cb55275f1b6f2b514b4f9
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-26 15:49:38 +0100

    terminal: Fix handling of escape keys
    
    After an escape key sequence, the key up event of the last key should
    not be sent to the emulated machine.

commit 61801b5ac8c83aef29631f139c53105d795875bb
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-21 16:34:39 +0200

    macplus: Fix keypad to motion key mapping
    
    There is now a config file option to map the host keypad keys to
    either the Mac keypad or to Mac motion keys.
    
    The mapping itself was totally screwd up and should be fixed now.

commit e956ce34f02ee05756656235f281dad651673a23
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-19 15:40:47 +0200

    Document the character drivers and their options

