Date:   2009-10-19 15:36:43 +0200

    char: Add a TCP character driver

commit cfeddced68dd57a11e2ba92c4074a0951fd299ec
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-19 15:05:43 +0200

    macplus: More accurate video timing
    
    The video frame duration should not be calculated as a sum of a lot
    of very short intervals.

commit a989a32b05d0fc9e31805069e3269131b309ee85
Author: Hampa Hug <hampa@hampa.ch>
Date:   2009-10-19 12:31:04 +0200

    macplus: Remove the obsolete accurate mode
    
    The accurate mode is now the same as "speed = 1" except without
    synchronisation to real time. As such it's practically useless.

commit f1cae614050a3023e98d1ac4a607f1062cc53800
